Package index

Graph components

add_e61_logo()
Add e61 logo to graph
add_baseline()
Adds a thin black line
labs_e61()
Add graph titles and footers in the e61 style
plot_label() plab()
Add on-graph labels to graphs
geom_pointbar()
Custom geom combining points and error bars

Formatting

format_flip()
Applies changes to the theme for horizontal bar graphs
save_e61()
Save graphs with theme61 styles and defaults
square_legend_symbols()
Converts all legend colours to squares
theme_e61()
e61 themed graph options
theme_e61_alt()
e61 themed graph options in an alternative style
theme_e61_spatial()
e61 themed spatial maps options

Scales

scale_y_continuous_e61() scale_x_continuous_e61()
Format axes in the e61 style
scale_colour_e61() scale_fill_e61()
Colour and fill scales using colours from the e61 palette
scale_colour_e61_aus() scale_fill_e61_aus()
A consistent set of colours for Australian states and territories for graphing
sec_rescale_inv() sec_rescale()
Dual y-axis graphing functions

Maps

add_map_e61()
Add an underlying base map to ggplot maps
crop_aus_coord()
Crops maps of Australia to exclude outlying territories
setup_stadia_maps()
Setup Stadia Maps API
theme_e61_spatial()
e61 themed spatial maps options

Miscellaneous

e61_chart_maker()
An add-in to easily create plots with ggplot2
set_open_graph_browser() unset_open_graph_browser()
Set option to open graphs in the browser instead of the Viewer pane
set_format() unset_format()
Sets the default file save format if format is not specified
